Name: Sherpa Original Deluxe Pet Carriers
Description:
Sherpa Original Deluxe Pet Carriers
Travel in comfort and style with Carriers Airline Approved pet carriers. 
The patented spring wire frame allows the end of the carrier to be pushed down, conforming to under-seat requirements. 
Mesh panels offer proper ventilation and locking zippers for safety.
Top and side entries make it easier to comfortably load pets. 
The seat belt security strap doubles as a luggage strap.
PRODUCT DETAILS: 
Small: Animal weighing 3.6 kg and less 15″ L x 10″ W x 8.5″ H
Medium: Animal weighing 7.2 kg and less 17″ L x 11″ W x 10.5″ H
Large: Animal weighing 10 kg and less 19″ L x 11.75″ W x 11.5″ H
